  "audio": {
    "narration": [
      {
        "text": "我们来解这道关于圆的问题。题目给出：⊙O 的半径 OA 等于 5，半径 OC 与弦 AB 垂直，垂足为 D，且 OD 的长度为 3。要求我们求弦 AB 的长度。",
        "start_time": 0,
        "end_time": 10,
        "voice_config": {
          "speaker": "teacher_male",
          "speed": 1.0,
          "pitch": 1.0
        }
      },
      {
        "text": "根据垂径定理，半径 OC 垂直平分弦 AB，设 AD 和 DB 的长度都为 x。",
        "start_time": 10,
        "end_time": 18,
        "voice_config": {
          "speaker": "teacher_male",
          "speed": 1.0,
          "pitch": 1.0
        }
      },
      {
        "text": "在直角三角形 OAD 中，根据勾股定理，OA 的平方等于 OD 的平方加上 AD 的平方。",
        "start_time": 18,
        "end_time": 28,
        "voice_config": {
          "speaker": "teacher_male",
          "speed": 1.0,
          "pitch": 1.0
        }
      },
      {
        "text": "代入已知数据，5 的平方等于 3 的平方加上 x 的平方。",
        "start_time": 28,
        "end_time": 35,
        "voice_config": {
          "speaker": "teacher_male",
          "speed": 1.0,
          "pitch": 1.0
        }
      },
      {
        "text": "计算可得，25 等于 9 加上 x 的平方，从而 x 的平方等于 16，x 等于 4。",
        "start_time": 35,
        "end_time": 45,
        "voice_config": {
          "speaker": "teacher_male",
          "speed": 1.0,
          "pitch": 1.0
        }
      },
      {
        "text": "因为 AD 和 DB 的长度都为 x，所以弦 AB 的长度为 2x，即 2 乘以 4，等于 8。",
        "start_time": 45,
        "end_time": 55,
        "voice_config": {
          "speaker": "teacher_male",
          "speed": 1.0,
          "pitch": 1.0
        }
      },
      {
        "text": "因此，弦 AB 的长度为 8。",
        "start_time": 55,
        "end_time": 60,
        "voice_config": {
          "speaker": "teacher_male",
          "speed": 1.0,
          "pitch": 1.0
        }
      }
